name: Emily Humphrey
text: So Google says they are open till 3 on Saturdays but i went by at 2 today and they are closed. The sign on the door has saturday painted out. So thats the only reason im writing a review.

name: Jim Landers
text: Munford Pawn primarily takes firearms and gold/silver etc. Rarely do they buy anything else, other than precious medals, but may be some exceptions.

name: Keith Byram
text: They are great with service and prices and are just great honest people.
